Notebook[{
Cell["\<\
Note: this is not the final product anymore; I\[CloseCurlyQuote]ve \
manipulated this document from what I originally submitted so that I could \
have a better understanding of working with Mathematica. A pdf copy of the \
original document can be found in the HW6 folder.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.857660764006263*^9, 3.857660848246789*^9}, {
  3.857661046555238*^9, 
  3.8576610621591787`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"94ab8825-4603-4564-a49d-\
b56171f5c58c"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Homework 6 Plots", "Title",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.855972129947721*^9, 
  3.855972159581374*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"6db68070-1e13-4c59-a096-\
1c7497b353e6"],

Cell["\<\
Adam Prieto, Ben Lee, and Mariah Archuleta 
Professor Shelley Poole
14 March 2022\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.856061036716709*^9, 3.8560610912294683`*^9}, {
  3.8562000071864367`*^9, 
  3.85620001042126*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"b73538a0-107f-4386-bbd7-\
8e3acdd94dbd"],

Cell["3.6 Problems", "Subtitle",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.855972349952901*^9, 
  3.855972354122764*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"0f311283-11df-480e-9847-\
24e904ac7a68"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[TextData[{
 "Plot all solutions to the Heat Equation: ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    SubscriptBox["u", "t"], "=", 
    RowBox[{"k", "*", 
     SubscriptBox["u", "xx"]}]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "6bc83132-d274-45a8-bb90-e0a38ab7396d"],
 ". Evaluate the solutions and their behaviors. Discuss characteristics and \
similarities. "
}], "Chapter",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.855972173283491*^9, 3.855972262913926*^9}, {
  3.855972656151338*^9, 
  3.855972678345429*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"7ccee061-ecb6-4ea5-94e9-\
7f006a812cce"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["a.) u(0,t) = 0, u(1,t) = 1, f(x) = x, k = 2, and L = 1", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8559722724750967`*^9, 3.855972316956791*^9}, 
   3.8559723761421213`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"f198b00a-eb06-4685-b66c-\
cb0ba4897da1"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "For this problem, I obtained the general solution \[LongDash] u(x,t) = x \
\[LongDash] by solving for a particular linear equation and generalizing that \
equation for x and t. It\[CloseCurlyQuote]s worth noting that the solution to \
this problem is identical to the problem presented in the notes. That said, \
this answer shouldn\[CloseCurlyQuote]t be surprising since we generalized ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    SubscriptBox["u", "p"], "(", 
    RowBox[{"x", ",", "t"}], ")"}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "a6c3027e-a068-43a5-a4d7-7a48f09b246c"],
 " in class and in the notes. It\[CloseCurlyQuote]s also worth noting that \
this problems is identical to the example problem that was worked out in \
class. "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.856060255117199*^9, 3.856060362255085*^9}, {
  3.8560604433218*^9, 3.85606060654713*^9}, {3.856060922718914*^9, 
  3.8560609584413137`*^9}, {3.856201162496353*^9, 
  3.8562011867701178`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"8af9faa6-5ef0-4284-9f13-\
89bbca89ea1d"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"Jenna", "=", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     SubscriptBox["u", "11"], "[", 
     RowBox[{"x_", ",", "t_"}], "]"}], "=", "x"}]}], ";"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.856060775353498*^9, 3.8560607992196617`*^9}},
 CellLabel->"In[3]:=",ExpressionUUID->"8869f4db-a18e-4b8d-be8c-4733c1b24b73"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"Plot3D", "[", 
  RowBox[{"Jenna", ",", 
   RowBox[{"{", 
    RowBox[{"x", ",", "0", ",", "5"}], "}"}], ",", 
   RowBox[{"{", 
    RowBox[{"t", ",", "0", ",", "5"}], "}"}], ",", 
   RowBox[{"Mesh", "\[Rule]", "Automatic"}], ",", 
   RowBox[{"MeshStyle", "\[Rule]", "Automatic"}], ",", 
   RowBox[{"PlotTheme", "\[Rule]", "\"\<Marketing\>\""}], ",", 
   RowBox[{"PlotLegends", "\[Rule]", " ", "\"\<Expressions\>\""}], ",", 
   RowBox[{"PlotLabel", "\[Rule]", "\"\<Jenna\>\""}]}], "]"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.856060817089271*^9, 3.856060817887123*^9}, {
  3.8560609928722277`*^9, 3.8560609937580748`*^9}, {3.8560611114420843`*^9, 
