Cell["\<\
Here, we can observe what happens when we have both a homogeneous and \
particular solution since the above graph has the downward slope of the \
particular solution and the sinusoidal behavior of the fourier series.  In \
short, it looks like what we would expect the product of two functions would \
look like. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.856201338118721*^9, 3.856201439012555*^9}, {
  3.856307923538197*^9, 
  3.856307944131167*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"2aee4b26-818e-48d7-b945-\
56d60c6457b7"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[TextData[{
 "c.) u(0,t) = 0, ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["u", "x"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "811e7cb2-862e-4abd-98f9-993e4a75233b"],
 "(\[Pi],t) = 0, f(x) = Sin[x], k = 3, and L = \[Pi]\nThese are the correct, \
updated conditions that we discussed in Office Hours. "
}], "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.855972411763204*^9, 3.855972447104456*^9}, {
   3.856284989052425*^9, 3.856284989435995*^9}, 3.856285047003457*^9, {
   3.856304055718354*^9, 
   3.856304092826705*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"22ac145d-4c2f-4a51-929a-\
191e0c0bf4eb"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "First, it\[CloseCurlyQuote]s important to point out that the original \
problem had a typo in that ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     SubscriptBox["u", "x"], "(", 
     RowBox[{"\[Pi]", ",", "t"}], ")"}], "=", " ", "0"}], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"c1b59ef3-5366-4dfa-a674-de27e91a2810"],
 " is the correct initial condition while ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     SubscriptBox["u", "x"], "(", 
     RowBox[{"\[Pi]", ",", "t"}], ")"}], "=", " ", 
    RowBox[{"-", "1"}]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "1ab8aced-77cb-498b-b73c-6c8e88b129b0"],
 " was initially given. That aside, this problem exhibits Homogeneous Neumann \
Conditions and can be solved as such; our final solution being ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"u", "(", 
     RowBox[{"x", ",", "t"}], ")"}], "=", 
    RowBox[{"2", 
     SuperscriptBox["\[ExponentialE]", 
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"-", "3"}], "t"}]], "*", 
     RowBox[{"Cos", "[", "x", "]"}]}]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "bf70ef4b-61cd-405b-a4d9-b1b79b17b8b2"],
 ". "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.856285019969318*^9, 3.8562851121093693`*^9}, {
  3.856285190796624*^9, 3.856285223547344*^9}, {3.856285266073804*^9, 
  3.856285332596003*^9}, {3.8563041136472692`*^9, 
  3.8563041178359203`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"2bcd27f6-8680-40be-9db8-\
20fd224b62a9"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"Yana", "=", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     SubscriptBox["u", "3"], "[", 
     RowBox[{"x_", ",", "t_"}], "]"}], "=", 
    RowBox[{"2", "*", 
     SuperscriptBox["\[ExponentialE]", 
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"-", "3"}], "t"}]], "*", 
     RowBox[{"Cos", "[", "x", "]"}]}]}]}], ";"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.856285359227158*^9, 3.8562854197372723`*^9}},
 CellLabel->"In[7]:=",ExpressionUUID->"7a1f2fae-4361-4fcf-8abe-b8872f8bbc2b"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"Plot3D", "[", 
  RowBox[{"Yana", ",", 
   RowBox[{"{", 
    RowBox[{"x", ",", "0", ",", "5"}], "}"}], ",", 
   RowBox[{"{", 
    RowBox[{"t", ",", "0", ",", ".2"}], "}"}], ",", 
   RowBox[{"Mesh", "\[Rule]", "Automatic"}], ",", 
   RowBox[{"MeshStyle", "\[Rule]", "Automatic"}], ",", 
   RowBox[{"PlotTheme", "\[Rule]", "\"\<Marketing\>\""}], ",", 
   RowBox[{"PlotLegends", "\[Rule]", " ", "\"\<Expressions\>\""}], ",", 
   RowBox[{"PlotLabel", "\[Rule]", "\"\<Yana\>\""}]}], "]"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.85628543452102*^9, 3.856285455422903*^9}, {
   3.856285598639473*^9, 3.856285644289105*^9}, {3.856285707120904*^9, 
