Cell["\<\
In the above graph, we can clearly see the exponential decay and also briefly \
see the beginning of the sinusoidal behavior as the graph begins to go back \
up as x increases. It\[CloseCurlyQuote]s also worth noting that both b and c \
exhibit visual sinusoidal behavior since both solutions are partially \
composed of sinusoidal terms. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.856285689821981*^9, 3.8562857038100777`*^9}, {
  3.856285759761795*^9, 
  3.856285960361711*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"69e9678b-817d-4cb8-afe6-\
47f10d054206"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[TextData[{
 "d.) ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["u", "x"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "a0458563-b713-48d3-8aff-8d6a48108d04"],
 "(0,t) = 0, ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["u", "x"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "b938111a-7a65-4adc-898e-09b2dd4759ac"],
 "(2,t) = 0, f(x) = 3Cos[2\[Pi]t], k = ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   FractionBox["1", "2"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "9f0a6a59-f75d-48da-b650-63cc00d437b7"],
 ", and L = 2"
}], "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.855972462685804*^9, 
  3.855972514477953*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"b894157b-073f-44bc-b740-\
91b15f056ae1"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "For this problem, I obtained the general solution \[LongDash] ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"u", "(", 
     RowBox[{"x", ",", "t"}], ")"}], "=", 
    RowBox[{"3", 
     RowBox[{"Cos", "[", 
      RowBox[{"2", "\[Pi]", "*", "x"}], "]"}], "*", 
     SuperscriptBox["\[ExponentialE]", 
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"-", "2"}], 
       SuperscriptBox["\[Pi]", "2"], "*", "t"}]]}]}], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"8e02e310-4740-4a4e-901c-92e482a748ba"],
 " \[LongDash] by applying the technique for Homogenous Neumann Conditions. \
Since this solution is not represented by a series, plotting this function \
should be a little easier.  "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8560598195653467`*^9, 3.856059869540485*^9}, {
  3.856059905383234*^9, 
  3.856060030110668*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"cc93c80d-946d-469d-8199-\
1fd0779bf776"],

